Jennifer Lopez has stripped naked while promoting her pricey “booty balm”. The star showed off her incredible physique as she struck a sultry pose in the stunning photos. The 53-year-old looked impossibly toned in the photos, which were released alongside a video of the star in a black cutout swimsuit. It’s all to help promote her Firm + Flaunt “targeted booty balm” by JLo Beauty. On the product website, it promises: “A clinically tested, high-performance formula inspired by the most iconic booty that visibly firms and hydrates skin and fades the appearance of stretch marks for a smoother, more refined-looking booty.” But those who want a bottom like JLo’s will need to part with £54 first.